<h1 id="russia-advance-holders-overview" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="28">Russia advance holders overview</h1>

<h2 id="set-up-parameters-for-advance-holders" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="31">Set up parameters for advance holders</h2>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">Accounts payable</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">Setup</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">Accounts payable parameters</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">Advance holders</strong> tab, in the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">Posting profile</strong> field, select the default posting profile that should be used to complete transactions for advance holders.</p>
<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="37">For more information, see the &quot;Set up posting profiles for accounting vouchers&quot; section later in this topic.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Set the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Set default advance holder</strong> option to <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Yes</strong> to set the current user as the advance holder.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Set the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Advance holder sorting</strong> option to <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Yes</strong> to show advance holders at the top of the grid on the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Advance holders</strong> page.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">Set the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">Issue when balance is open</strong> option to <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">Yes</strong> to allow cash advances to be issued to advance holders who have an open positive balance.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">Set the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">Automatic settlement</strong> option to <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">Yes</strong> if automatic transactions settlement is required.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="43"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="43">Set the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="43">Settlement by profile</strong> option to <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="43">Yes</strong> to settle transactions only with an identical posting profile.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Balance closing</strong> FastTab, under <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Balance closing via cash</strong>, in the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Name</strong> field, select the cash slip journal code. This journal code is used to generate cash disbursement slips and reimbursement slips when an advance holder's balances are closed through cash.</p>
<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">All journals are of the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Cash</strong> type.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49">Cash</strong> field, select the cash account to determine the vouchers that are used to close the balances for the advance holder.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Under <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Balance closing via bank</strong>, in the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Name</strong> field, select the journal code for transactions to close the balances through a bank.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">Account type</strong> field, select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">Bank</strong> to close the balances for an advance holder through a bank.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">Main account</strong> field, select the bank account code to close the balances for an advance holder through a bank.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">Number sequences</strong> tab, define number sequences codes for the following references:</p>
<ul sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">Advance report</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="56">Advance report voucher</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57">Settlement voucher</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Exchange adjustment voucher (Advance holders)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">Save</strong>, or close the page.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="set-up-an-advance-holder-group" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">Set up an advance holder group</h2>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64">You must create an advance holder group to group advance holders. For example, you can group advance holders by vouchers that are calculated in a single account.</p>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">Accounts payable</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">Setup</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">Advance holders</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">Advance holder groups</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">New</strong> to create a new advance holder group or <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">Edit</strong> to adjust an existing group.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68">Group</strong> field, enter the code for the advance holder group.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">Description</strong> field, enter a description of the advance holder group.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">Offset account</strong> field, select the general ledger offset account to use for the advance holder group.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Save</strong>, or close the page.</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="set-up-posting-profiles-for-accounting-vouchers" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="73">Set up posting profiles for accounting vouchers</h2>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="75">You can set up the following posting profiles for an account of operations:</p>
<ul sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">One ledger account for all advance holders</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="78">A separate ledger account for each group of advance holders</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="79">A separate ledger account for each advance holder</li>
</ul>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81">Accounts payable</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81">Setup</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81">Advance holders</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81">Employee posting profiles</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="82"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="82">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="82">New</strong> to create a new posting profile or <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="82">Edit</strong> to adjust an existing profile.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">Posting profile</strong> field, enter the profile ID of the posting profile that is being processed.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="84"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="84">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="84">Description</strong> field, enter a description of the posting profile.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Table restrictions</strong> FastTab, in the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Allow empty dimension value</strong> field, select the condition under which settlements that are related to accruals and closing payment operations can be processed if dimension values aren't specified. The following options are available:</p>
<ul sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87"><strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">No</strong> – Transactions aren't settled, regardless of whether the dimension values are specified.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88"><strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="88">Auto</strong> – Automatic transactions are settled, regardless of whether the dimension values are specified.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="89"><strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="89">Manual</strong> – Manual transactions are settled, regardless of whether the dimension values are specified.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90"><strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90">Always</strong> – All transactions are settled, regardless of whether the dimension values are specified.</li>
</ul>
<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="93">This field lets you ignore the values of dimensions when individual transactions are created.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="95"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="95">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="95">Setup</strong> FastTab, select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="95">Add</strong> to create a new record for posting profile details.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="96"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="96">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="96">Valid for</strong> field, select the level of grouping for the setup of the posting profile. The following options are available:</p>
<ul sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="98">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="98"><strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="98">Table</strong> – This option is set for only one advance holder.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="99"><strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="99">Group</strong> – This option is set for a group of advance holders.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="100"><strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="100">All</strong> – This option is set for all advance holders.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="102"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="102">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="102">Reference</strong> field, select the corresponding reference.</p>
<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="104">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="105">You can select a value in this field only if you selected <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="105">Table</strong> or <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="105">Group</strong> in the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="105">Valid for</strong> field.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="107"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="107">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="107">Summary account</strong> field, select the account that should reflect transactions for the advance holders.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="108"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="108">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="108">Set</strong> field, select the dimension focus for settlement control.</p>
<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="110">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="111">The specified dimension set indicates that dimension control is activated.</p>
</div>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="113"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="113">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="113">Save</strong>, or close the page.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="set-up-the-terms-of-payment" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="115">Set up the terms of payment</h2>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="117">You must set up the terms of payment when you register the purchase of goods from a vendor through an advance holder. The advance holder makes the purchase.</p>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">Accounts payable</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">Payment setup</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">Terms of payment</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="120">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="120">New</strong> to create a new terms of payment record or <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="120">Edit</strong> to adjust an existing record.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="121">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="121">Terms of payment</strong> field, enter the code for the terms of payment.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="122">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="122">Description</strong> field, enter a description of the terms of payment.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="123">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="123">Setup</strong> FastTab, in the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="123">Payment method</strong> field, select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="123">C.O.D.</strong></li>
