<h2 id="set-up-the-per-diem-expense-rates" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="128">Set up the per diem expense rates</h2>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="130">Expense rates are used to generate an advance report for per diem expenses. They are also used for automatic calculation of standard and over-rate amounts.</p>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="132">
