<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="134">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="134">Expense</strong> field, enter the expense code.</li>
