<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136">Rate</strong> field, enter the standard established value for this expense.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137">Currency</strong> field, select the currency code that operations for this expense are registered in.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">Setup</strong> FastTab, under <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">Rate</strong>, in the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-advance-holders.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">Main account</strong> field, select the accounting statement that should reflect normal charges.</li>
